				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text{Free radical scavenging effect }}\% = [(A_{0} - A_{1} )/A_{0} ]\times 100.$$\end{document} (A0 = the control absorbance and A1 = the sample solution absorbance).
